com.teamdev.jxmaps

Class MapTypeStyler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxmaps.MapObject
      • com.teamdev.jxmaps.MapTypeStyler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class MapTypeStyler
extends MapObject
    Represents map type styler. A styler affects how a map's elements will be styled. Each MapTypeStyler should contain one and only one key. If more than one key is specified in a single MapTypeStyler, all but one will be ignored.
